{"tid":1393595,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【守護下一代  為良知發聲】","createTime":"2019-08-01T06:47:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T07:23:15.000Z","uid":38075,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fc8bd7d5986909ba97513c61d8af1402c5e625dd","tid":1393595,"uid":38075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:47:59.000Z","msg":"呼籲教師響應8.5罷工 8.17教師遊行<br />\n<br />\n過去兩個月，香港人多次走上街頭，就《逃犯條例》修訂所觸發的群眾運動提出五大訴求，可是政府仍然置若罔聞，更任由警民衝突日益加劇。警方處理大型示威的手法屢受批評，不單多次使用過量武力引致大量市民受傷，更於元朗721暴徒襲擊市民事件不見影蹤。<br />\n<br />\n面對社會訴求，政府沒有認真回應，更不惜以暴動、非法集結、阻差辦公等罪名，向示威者作出政治檢控，當中有教師，更有為數不少的年輕人。政府急於以數年甚至十年刑期的罪名威嚇港人，卻遲遲未有對在元朗無差別襲擊市民的暴徒作出起訴，更惹起市民質疑政府司法不公。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，教育界在這段期間屢受攻擊，有教師因於私人領域發表言論而遭受親建制傳媒攻擊，前特首梁振英更以公職名義發信施壓，要求學校辭退有關教師，實際上在教育界造成白色恐怖的氣氛。<br />\n<br />\n教協對現時的局勢深感痛心，同時對於以上種種事件感到十分憤怒。對於有市民發起8月5日全港大罷工，教協呼籲全港教職員響應。另外，教協將於8月17日發起教育界遊行，我們呼籲教師積極參與。<br />\n<br />\n為了對抗白色恐怖，守護我城的下一代，教師更要在此時刻為良知發聲。<br />\n<br />\n就8月5日全港罷工的詳情，請同工參閱以下網址：<a href=\"http://www.hkptu.org/61346\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkptu.org%2F61346&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5xq8xf71D2STVxQEH8iwqLk%3D&h=072a12b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.hkptu.org/61346</a><br />\n<br />\n我們正處理有關8月17日教育界遊行的工作及申請不反對通知書，遊行詳情將容後公佈。<br />\n請留意教協facebook及telegram channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hkptu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkptu&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5xq8xf71D2STVxQEH8iwqLk%3D&h=2ed63010\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkptu</a><br />\n<br />\n#教協 #HKPTU #8月5罷工 #817教師大遊行<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2880005635407693&amp;id=292234587518157\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2880005635407693%26id%3D292234587518157&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5xq8xf71D2STVxQEH8iwqLk%3D&h=11f24f3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2880005635407693&amp;id=292234587518157</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9bU8iiN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9bU8iiN.png&h=945827f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9ae7eb12254ba10e51376fe103df6e3eef2095b","tid":1393595,"uid":38075,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:48:18.000Z","msg":"你想過嗎？<br />\n現今的年青人在做什麼？<br />\n為甚麼他們要擔驚受怕？<br />\n為甚麼他們要在街頭流淚流血？<br />\n你以為他們不怕痛？<br />\n你以為他們不知道有機會要在牢獄中渡過最青春的十年？<br />\n作為未來教育工作者的你，<br />\n無忘初心，與孩子同行，<br />\n守護香港的良知，守護學生的未來。<br />\n<br />\n8月2日 晚上7 時 中環遮打花園見<br />\n8月5日 全城三罷 七區集會<br />\n8月17&nbsp; 教協教師集會<br />\n<br />\n伴學子，憑良知，行公義，護法治。<br />\n Link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFClJ47fhJzsgC3JBw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAFClJ47fhJzsgC3JBw&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5xq8xf71D2STVxQEH8iwqLk%3D&h=d8a1895e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFClJ47fhJzsgC3JBw</a>"},{"pid":"acccf585f6ba2c6106a6e6d615e0d7476b81943b","tid":1393595,"uid":292881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:48:45.000Z","msg":"Pushhh"},{"pid":"8a88dfddb48c4f24dc635e6f6603df2e90718223","tid":1393595,"uid":38075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:48:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a361eca44087d76590bc6b9a4ea4cf8d33dce0c","tid":1393595,"uid":38075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:49:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4c69bedcd99aa9fae62c15f46afd707e211bcbe","tid":1393595,"uid":167808,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:49:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/98LCV6h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F98LCV6h.png&h=e03548b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bdb0454814bfe06906b6274a86da8116b14d88e4","tid":1393595,"uid":269285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:51:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4712dd0a8213aa6663b7dc1934d832fc82cfd8d","tid":1393595,"uid":3